cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.NE 

The paper introduces a hybrid model that combines the representation power of generative models with the learning capabilities of neural networks for structured data. This makes it likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), computer vision (cs.CV), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
